title: Added option to remove app icon from launcher (to avoid clutter).
message:
Added option to remove app icon from launcher (to avoid clutter).

Unfortunately, I can't find an easy way that the user can undo that action
without uninstalling and reinstalling the app.

One idea would be to add a low-priority notification that appears whenever a
USB connection is established.
